#Sum of digits of a number:

#Taking input:
n = int(input('Enter a number'))
p = 0

#Logic:
while(n > 0):
    q = n % 10
    p = p + q
    n = n//10


#Printing result:
print('The total sum of digits is: ',p)

Output:

